e alive but they couldn't the mob was just too tough. She also wanted to know why I hadn't responded to tells. Then she said something about getting a guide to move me to arena. I log back in and I am in lake Rathetear arena, and I am thinking this is strange, check the inventory and I am naked, this is even stranger. I look at the exp bar and I am halfway through 52, ok now I am really MAD. I also cannot remember where I originally camped out. The friend who sent me the email was not on. So I finally remember where I camped out and get over there. Loot everything but one item then I check the corpse timer and it says resurrection time has expired. So I finally make the connection, I had camped out something hit me, and I died and went to my bind point. Had fired off a nasty /petition because I was sure I had been hacked. Get to my bind point and there nicely stacked at 8 bodies. I check a body and there is some sort of totem on it that I had never seen or heard of. So about this time I get a tell from a guide, explain what had happened and everything I knew. Guide thought I was making it up and had no idea what totem was, so this monk comes out to survey the damage. Sees the bodies examines the totem and then proceeds to res the 8 bodies. Thank goodness because of the patch the timer didn't expire. 100% resses and I managed to get my level back.<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :rollin --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/roll.gif ALT=":rollin"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
<br>
I figure and this is not 100% sure that when I /campdesktop I disconnected but my char did not. He must have stood there for awhile before something happened upon him. And got killed then at my bind point my friends saw something hitting me and not responding (they assumed I had fallen asleep, they petitioned and the guide said the only thing he could do is move me.) We were hunting in the area and they were going back to our spot to hunt some more saw the pile of bodies and took action. The only thing I can think of for the totem is it is something the server puts on bodies before the patch so they don't poof. The guide who helped res my bodies was wonderful and I finally calmed down. My bind point since then has been in the city of shadowhaven. Don't want to take any chances. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  I campout by clicking every one of those silly buttons. <br>
<br>
Also it is a lot easier to trust people now in game, because now there aren’t a whole lot of bad things they can do to your body. Was a time in game when if you typed /consent  they could take things off your body. So there were more than a few horror stories associated with that. Now if you type /consent all they can do is drag your body. Also asking for help in game can &quot;generally&quot; get you some higher levels who remember all too well these younger days. My druid has done many a corpse run to help someone. Had a high level necro pull a link dead corpse out of the giant fort in frontier mountains. That one I zoned into Frontier Mountains from Lake of Ill Omen, started to run towards the giant fort. YOU HAVE BEEN DISCONNECTED. Then for 15 mins got the you have an char logged in message.  Ahhh the memories!<br>
